## Syntax Highlighting

Check out this Swift code with beautiful syntax highlighting:

```swift
struct Person {
    let name: String
    var age: Int

    func greet() {
        print("Hello, my name is \(name)!")
    }
}

let person = Person(name: "Name", age: 20)
person.greet()
```

